summary:
I have acquired CAP master's diploma in 2022 and am looking for teaching positions.
I have experience in:
- Teaching music (all ages)
-  High-school teaching (humanities)
- Teaching English as a second language (have worked in English academies 2018-2021). This includes Cambridge exam preparation for all levels, as well as IELTS preparation, working on the pronunciation and conversational English.
- Teaching online
- Lesson planning and preparation for various formats
- Arranging and composing music
- Editing videos (you can see the results on my YouTube channel here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKRfF8w5KcARQ8aeuvqaJdw)
